data.description: Welcome! Great location! Adjacent to Pennypack Park. This home is situated in a quiet cul-de-sac in the highly sought after community of Fox Chase.  Make sure you turned into "TABOR Terr". The house is @ top of the court on your right. Main entrance on the right side of the home. This spacious home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a huge outdoor space for entertainment. It also offers a stylish modern eat in kitchen with quartz countertops. The kitchen space also has a built-in breakfast bar.  Also has an ample formal dining room, a living room and 1/2 bathroom @ top of basement steps. The basement has a large family room, exit to patio, large storage space and hallway to utility room, laundry & exit to driveway and garage.
